How to use the Unit Tests

1) Add a new class to the Unit Test Project (PsychicNinjaUnitTest)
2) A new test is a function, that goes in your new test class, following this format

[Fact]
public void ClassBeingTested_WhatYou'reTesting_Test()
{
    Do_Some_Setup();

	Do_Action_Being_Tested();

	Assert(Action_Being_Tested_Had_The_Right_Result);
}

3) Right-click PsychicNinjaUnitTest and say Build and Run.
